'''罗马圣依纳爵堂'''（{{lang-it|Chiesa di Sant'Ignazio di Loyola a Campo Marzio}}, {{lang-la| S. Ignatii de Loyola in Campo Martio}}）是意大利罗马的一座[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]聖堂，主保圣人是[[耶稣会|耶稣会]]的创始人[[依纳爵·罗耀拉|依纳爵·罗耀拉]]。这座聖堂为[[巴洛克|巴洛克]]风格，兴建于1626年到1650年。这座聖堂最初是毗邻的罗马学院的聖堂，1584年罗马学院搬进较大的新建筑，成为[[宗座额我略大学|宗座额我略大学]]<ref name="OW">{{cite web|url=http://www.chiesasantignazio.org/|title=Official Website of the Church of St Ignatius of Loyola at Campus Martius|last=Society of Jesus|accessdate=2009-01-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211232809/http://www.chiesasantignazio.org/|archivedate=2008-12-11}}</ref>。該聖堂現在也作為司鐸級樞機的[[領銜聖堂|領銜聖堂]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=S. Ignazio di Loyola a Campo Marzio (Cardinal Titular Church)|url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/d1i01.html|publisher=Catholic-hierarchy.org|accessdate=2012-09-17|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612030623/http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/d1i01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==

罗马学院在1551年初创时颇为简陋。1560年，Vittoria della Tolfa<ref>{{cite journal|last=Valone|first=C.|date=2003-07-16|title=Architecture as a public voice for women in sixteenth-century Rome|journal=Renaissance Studies|publisher=Blackwell Publishing Ltd|volume=15|issue=3|pages=301-327|doi=10.1111/1477-4658.00372 }}</ref>, {{lang|it|Marchesa}} della Valle，将整个街区和建筑物捐献给[[耶稣会|耶稣会]]创办罗马学院<ref name="bail">{{cite book | last = Bailey | first = Gauvin | title = Between Renaissance and Baroque | publisher = University of Toronto Press | location = Toronto | year = 2003 | isbn = 0802037216 | page = 112 | chapter = Jesuit Teaching and a Brief History of the Roman Collegiate Institutions | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=suRw3StCpEEC&pg=PA112 | quote = ''The Collegio was set back on its feet by Gregory XIII (1573-85), a pope for whom education was a primary concern (...).  Gregory reluctantly agreed to be called 'founder' of the college, a title offered in acknowledgment of his generosity, even though he thought it more properly belonged to the Marchesa della Valle. (...)'' | access-date = 2009-05-18 | archive-date = 2017-02-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170220020909/https://books.google.com/books?id=suRw3StCpEEC&pg=PA112 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，这一捐赠在为[[贫穷修女会|贫穷修女会]]捐建修女院之前 <ref> Bailey. p 112.</ref>。建造地点是罗马帝国时期[[艾西斯|艾西斯]]神庙的所在地<ref>The present façade stands where the Roman [[aqueduct|aqueduct]] [[Acqua_Vergine|Acqua Vergine]] once flowed down in a cascade.</ref> <ref name="OW"/>.

1626年8月2日举行了奠基仪式，到1650年拆除了老聖堂为巨大的新依纳爵堂让路，到该世纪末完成时，占据了整个街区。

== 内部 ==

这座聖堂呈拉丁十字平面，两侧有许多小礼拜堂。这座建筑受到了耶稣会母堂，罗马[[耶稣堂|耶稣堂]]（完成于16世纪后期）的启发。庄严的科林斯壁柱，作为戏剧性焦点的装饰华丽的祭台，彩色大理石，栩栩如生的人像，大量的镀金，制造出极为华丽的效果。

=== 波佐的壁画 ===

1685年，耶稣会會士[[安德里亚·波佐|安德里亚·波佐]]绘制了中殿天花板上壮观的壁画<ref name="cathency">{{CathEncy| wstitle=Andreas Pozzo| title =Andrea Pozzo| first =G. | last = Gietmann| authorlink = | accessdate =2009-01-31}}</ref>，描绘圣依纳爵在天国受到基督和圣母的欢迎，四大洲环绕在旁。
